<p>Thatâ€™s it! If all goes well running <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">bundle exec jekyll serve</code> should spin-up your site. If you encounter any bumps please file an issue on GitHub and make sure to indicate youâ€™re testing the pre-release Ruby gem version.</p>

